comments: Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hunter (ATL) and firms up and absorbs the contact.
Collins (ATL) makes contact to the arm of Fournier (ORL) that affect his SQBR.
Young (ATL) makes contact to the head of Fournier (ORL) on the jump shot attempt.
Collins (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ross (ORL), firms up and absorbs the contact.
Fultz (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Young (ATL).
Ross (ORL) wraps his right arm around the body of Collins (ATL) and holds him while setting the screen, affecting his ability to defend.
Huerter (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Vucevic (ORL) and makes a clean block. Collins (ATL) legally contest the shot attempt.
Carter (ATL) makes incidental contact with Ross (ORL) as makes contact with the loose ball.
Hunter (ATL) slides his arm across Vucevic's (ORL) front without affecting his FOM.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hunter (ATL) firms up, and absorbs the contact.
Fultz (ORL) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Collins (ATL) makes marginal contact to the body of Fournier (ORL) during his shooting motion at the rim.
Fournier (ORL) commits a take foul on Collins (ATL). The contact from Fournier forces Collins to step out of bounds.
